reviewText: a geate action euro crime movie.

Transfer looks like s***. Riddled with digital filtering artifacts turning everything into a noisy pointillistic mess. Yes, digital tools can be used to that effect. It was never intended but you can do it. Congratulations. Mission accomplished. Film destroyed.
An Italian policeman "Poliziotteschi" popular in the 1970s, this one is a lot like Dirty Harry, The French Connection, and Serpico.
